metadata.name: CryptoBurger
metadata.description: Cryptopunks was born 5 years ago. It represented the punk trend at that time. It was the product of the collision between contemporary art culture and the blockchain world. Today, 5 years later, I made this nft about hamburger with reference to Cryptopunks, hamburger As our traditional food, let it be combined with the nascent field of nft, written into the blockchain, written into history, and passed down forever !
